On Today's Dan Patrick Show Brady Quinn tells us which College Football Game he thinks is a trap game this weekend. Darius Rucker talks about the girl that "Let Her Cry" is based on. And Jeff Van Gundy explains what advice he'd give to Russell Westbrook.
